item.title: Order of The Arrow
item.description: Member, 2011 - Present Vice Chief of Program, Occoneechee Lodge 104, 2016-17 I have been a proud member of Boy Scouting’s National Honor Society, the Order of the Arrow, since 2011. In 2016, I had the honor of being elected as Occoneechee Lodge 104’s Vice Chief of Program. During my term, I had the opportunity to work with and learn from a great number of very passionate people, and lead them in service to our community.
